Sniper/Rhinox


Sniper went back to the base. He checked the Scanners and were 
surprise to see alot of blips at the Pred Base. "The Newcomers are 
attacking the Predacon Base." Sniper then contacted Iron Raptor.
"Iron 
Raptor, this is Sniper. The Predacon base is under attack by the 
Newcommers. Don't we have an alliance wiht The Predacons against the 
Newcommers or did that stop."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rhinox started working on the arks out hull. He mad a few Ajustment
to 
the armor. Made it a little stronger. He then started working on the 
plate of armor next to that. "Hmmm 1 down 5156 to go."
